/-!
# Examples: Licensing & Compliance Specification (LCS)

--**Source:** `spec/licensing/licensing_spec.md`
--**Status:** Complete
--**Last Updated:** 2026-01-16
--**Verified By:** Kilo Code

## Overview

This file contains concrete examples and test cases for Licensing & Compliance Specification, demonstrating SPDX identifiers, policy enforcement, build-time validation, and SBOM generation.

## Example Summary

| Example | Description | Status |
|---------|-------------|--------|
| `example_spdx_identifier_mit` | SPDX identifier for MIT | ✓ |
